race.comment: CAWBOURNE FOCUS (1) was speedy out of box 4 on debut to score by 5 lengths (19.73) at this track over 350m. Drawn to take advantage of good early pace. Looks the one to beat. ZIPPY ZENDEN (2) was out of placings last time (25.74) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing seventh and beaten 8 lengths. Can hit the frame with the right run. SPRING STEFFI (6) goes very well over this trip including two wins. Placed last time (24.85) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing third and beaten 4.5 lengths. Among the main chances. PRECOCIOUS STORM (3) form at this distance reads well.
